{"_path":"/maps/_biology/attention","_dir":"_biology","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"注意力","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"daily-bugs"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Daily Bugs"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_2026-01-10"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2026-01-10"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上周还是什么时候，我快速浏览了某篇文档，里面有A，但是我脑海里想的是B，就以为文档记录的是B。我特喵特意过了两遍文档，信誓旦旦和别人说B，结果是错的，后来才发现。这特喵是哪门子注意力啊！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"reports"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reports"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"注意力使用不完全报告"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sspai.com/post/70482","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力使用不完全报告"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在精神最佳、状态最好的时候完成最重要的任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"任务目标越清楚，大脑越容易进入专注状态。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用注意力会消耗体能，吃饱饭、睡好觉、多锻炼，都可以有效提升注意力的上限。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力不是恒定不变，而是在时刻波动的。短暂的跑神可以让大脑得到休息，要主动提醒自己回到焦点，保持专注。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力就像摄影，找到目标之后要通过"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立心理路径"}]},{"type":"text","value":"将焦点锁定，避免大脑受到其它元素干扰而脱离主线。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力和身体素质一样，越锻炼越强壮，越使用越熟练。"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"daily-bugs","depth":2,"text":"Daily Bugs"},{"id":"reports","depth":2,"text":"Reports"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_biology:attention.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_biology/attention.md","_stem":"6.maps/_biology/attention","_extension":"md"}